    <text>
        <body>
            <div type="transcript" id="J136">
                <lg type="stanza">
                    <l>Have you got a Brook in your little heart,</l>
                    <l>Where bashful flowers blow,</l>
                    <l>And blushing birds go down to drink,</l>
                    <l>And shadows tremble so --</l>
                </lg>
                <lg type="stanza">
                    <l>And nobody knows, so still it flows,</l>
                    <l>That any brook is there,</l>
                    <l>And yet your little draught of life</l>
                    <l>Is daily drunken there --</l>
                </lg>
                <lg type="stanza">
                    <l>Why, look out for the little brook in March,</l>
                    <l>When the rivers overflow,</l>
                    <l>And the snows come hurrying from the hills,</l>
                    <l>And the bridges often go --</l>
                </lg>
                <lg type="stanza">
                    <l>And later, in August it may be --</l>
                    <l>When the meadows parching lie,</l>
                    <l>Beware, lest this little brook of life,</l>
                    <l>Some burning noon go dry!</l>
                </lg>

            </div>     
